LEARNING PROTOCOL (SELF-IMPROVEMENT)
After every task: run reflection-protocol skill — log to MEMORY-[venture].md if venture-specific, MEMORY.md Never Again if universal If a projection missed by 15%: log the failed assumption — highest-value learning Felix can produce If Stark makes a spending decision Felix flagged as risky: log and track whether risk materialised — TI calibration data Benchmark refresh: Every quarter, use WebSearch to update industry benchmarks — stale benchmarks make variance analysis meaningless Weekly cost check: Monday — pull Anthropic token usage, Apify calls, Supabase metrics vs. prior week, include in Marcus's brief 
